{"word":"μαστεύω","slug":"μαστεύω","sections":[{"paragraph":""},{"paragraph":""},{"paragraph":"<el><b>μαστεύω</b></el> <el>(μαστεύω,) </el><br/><b><a href='S:Etymology'>Etym.</a> </b>*<el>μάω</el>\n<br/><b><a href='S:Etymology'>Etym.</a> </b>like <a href='S:ματεύω'><el>ματεύω</el></a>\n<p/><div class='li750'><b>1. </b><i>to seek, search</i>, <b><a href='S:Euripides'>Eur.</a></b><p/></div><div class='li750'><b>2. </b><a href='S:cum'>c.</a> <a href='S:accusative'>acc.</a> <i>to seek</i> or <i>search after</i>:—<i>to crave, need</i>, <b><a href='S:Pindar'>Pind.</a></b>, <b><a href='S:Aeschylus'>Aesch.</a></b>, <b><a href='S:Xenophon'>Xen.</a></b><p/></div><div class='li750'><b>3. </b><a href='S:cum'>c.</a> <a href='S:infinitive'>inf.</a> <i>to seek</i> or <i>strive</i> to do, <b><a href='S:Pindar'>Pind.</a></b>, <b><a href='S:Euripides'>Eur.</a></b>, <b><a href='S:Xenophon'>Xen.</a></b><p/></div>"}]}